cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.SY, cs.MM, cs.GT

Reasoning: 
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is the most likely category as the paper deals with network structure and management in cellular networks.
- cs.IT (Information Theory) is also likely as the paper uses stochastic geometry to calculate data rates and throughput.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper proposes a system for managing mobility in cellular networks.
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is relevant as the paper deals with data rates and throughput for mobile users.
- cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory) is less likely but still possible as the paper discusses joint optimization of network parameters.
